data.description: This charming property has undergone a thoughtful makeover, featuring updates like refreshed flooring, paint, modern appliances, improved windows, and a like new roof. The seamless open-concept design of the living, kitchen, and dining areas welcomes an abundance of natural light, creating a bright and inviting space. The bedroom layout is well designed, featuring a split floor plan for enhanced privacy. Outside, you'll discover a two-car garage, a useful storage shed, and a fully fenced private backyard, complete with dual elevated decks - ideal for enjoying your morning coffee or unwinding in the evenings. Residents can enjoy the array of amenities Battlement Mesa has to offer, including a spacious recreation center, a golf course with breathtaking mountain views, well-maintained hiking and biking trails, and convenient access to the Colorado River. Embrace all that this property and the community have to offer.
